  <brief_title>Observational Study to Observe the Efficacy of Levemir® (Insulin Detemir) in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Glycaemic Control After Initiation of Levemir® in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus and Time Period Between Diagnosis of Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus and Insulin Initiation.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
