  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients from general practice setting who have been deemed appropriate to receive Levemir®
        as part of routine out-patient care by the prescribing physician.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus

          -  Insulin-naive or currently treated with another basal insulin

          -  Inclusion of patients at the discretion of the treating physician after the decision
             to prescribe Levemir®

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 1 diabetes mellitus

          -  Patients treated with short acting or with premix insulin

          -  Women who are pregnant, breast feeding or have the intention to become pregnant

          -  Known or suspected allergy to the study product or related product

          -  Any exclusion criteria according to the Swiss Levemir® SPC (Summary of Product
             Characteristics)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
